item.title: About
item.description: Hi, my name is Autumn Haebig. I am a fifth year senior at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln currently double majoring in advertising and public relations and sports media and communication. I am a social media intern at SwimmingWorld Magazine, where I help run the Instagram, Twitter and LinkedIn. I’m also finishing off her swimming career for UNL and I’m serving as a two-time captain.
